about_me.about_me: The 2nd Workshop on the Evaluation of Generative Foundation Models at CVPR 2026
about_me.des: As Generative Foundation Models (GenFMs) continue to reshape the AI landscape, the need for robust evaluation methodologies has never been more critical. The 2nd Workshop on Evaluation for Generative Foundation Models at CVPR 2026 builds on the momentum of our successful first edition to address the evolving evaluation landscape.
